name: "Heavy Conversation" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Felt pen and colored pencil on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments.] Just look at the terror in those little guys' eyes. There's something about a number "10" floating in the black, black sky that has them horrified. I suppose it might bother me, too. After all, ten isn't even a prime number! (Gasp!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
